1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO ELIMINATE THE INTERIM DATE FOR CARBON REDUCTION BY
3 CERTAIN ELECTRIC PUBLIC UTILITIES, TO ALLOW AN ALTERNATIVE COST
4 RECOVERY MECHANISM FOR THE FINANCING COSTS OF CONSTRUCTION
5 WORK IN PROGRESS FOR BASELOAD ELECTRIC GENERATING FACILITIES, TO
6 MODIFY THE STATUTES GOVERNING COST RECOVERY FOR FUEL-RELATED
7 CHARGES AND PERFORMANCE-BASED RATEMAKING, AND TO CODIFY A
